criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria: at least one of the following criteria have to be present along with
        the need for a peripheral access

          -  chronic renal disease/ongoing dialysis;

          -  sickle cell anemia;

          -  prolonged and/or frequent use of i.v. drugs;

          -  difficult vascular access (after a first attempt or self-reported);

          -  previously need for more than one attempts / ultrasound guidance for getting a
             peripheral vascular access.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  no consent to participate in the study.
